Conclusion¶

Total sales is 22,97,200 and total profits are 2,86,397(12.47%).

Correlation between sales and profit is 0.48 (higher sales higher profits), While correlation between discount and profit is negative (higher discount lower will be profit).

Standard class is most commonly used mode of shipment.

Consumers are most significant segment for the business, it is good for business to launch schemes in consumer interest.

West region is giving maximum sales followed by east, central and south respectively.West region is giving maximum profits and sales. South have minimum sales and central region have minimum profits. West and east region are important for business.

California has the highest share of customers.

Binders, paper, furnishings , phones are important subcategories having maximum shares.

Sales and profit are maximum with 0 discount and profits become negative if discount rate is more than or equal to 0.3 Discounts should be minimised or removed to get more profits and sales. From the data, discounts are not benefiting the business even it is giving losses so discounts should be given with utmost care.

Technology have maximum sales and profits , furniture have very less profit as compared to sales so profit margin can be increased in furniture.

In furniture, chairs have maximum sales and profits while tables,bookcases have negative profit. In technology, copiers have maximum profit and sales while machines are giving minimum profits. In office supplies, papers giving highest sales and profit and supplies giving negative profits. All over, tables , bookcases and supplies give negative profits and copiers give maximum profits Tables and bookcases are the areas to be worked upon to minimise losses and can be sold as tying with chairs
